Priority: optional


Package: libdclass0-dev
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: file
Description: Device detection library written by Rezan Naghib
 Useragent device detection library written in C to quickly
 parse a browser's useragent string. The goal of this project
 is to quickly and accurately match text against a large number
 of flexable patterns.

